On Sun, Sep 27, 2009 at 10:32 PM, John Yust <yust(-at-)comcast.net> wrote:
 The only thing I haven't seen recommended that I think is really important
 is an oil filter. Add an oil filter to whatever engine you go with. Your
 engine will last a lot longer and you will have a lot more parts you can
 reuse when rebuild time finally comes if you have a filter.
